string.value: [TS_970109]_Backup data cannot be restored after reset.

string.name: reset_factory_dialog_retain_esim_content
string.value: [TS_1105212]_Your eSIM will remain stored on this device. Please keep it safe. If you no longer plan to use this device, please transfer your eSIM to another device or deactivate it. For instructions, contact your carrier.
